幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我用咗A mode<br />\n睇返張相， 當時係ISO 80, F7.1, 25s</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25s 都唔平? 你不如 po 張相上黎睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/151106_fd55705a7eda51453e3f0ab9ba25fc4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F151106_fd55705a7eda51453e3f0ab9ba25fc4c.jpg&h=1ff25b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見笑了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得依張 ok 喇喎<br />\n佢果日係大浪都無計, 除非落 ND 再曝長d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關事<br />\n係你個海距部機太遠,長曝分別唔大<br />\n即係咁，你問下國際太空站D人，個海平唔平？<br />\n你下次響海灘近D影一張試下<br />\n個人建議可以去下三家村個海灘仔，浪越大越好，有幾舊近海既石岩set高部機避開海水"},{"pid":"8d73a44c9da549c2c350f1edec2ebe10faf5e600","tid":23724,"uid":18228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪講緊倒影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係， 光嘅倒影嗰邊啲紋想再做好啲"},{"pid":"e5160a4343d2e61e37cb6ed0961f4fa5750e7ece","tid":23724,"uid":18228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我試過夜晚落腳架影維港，較咗細光圈長曝。<br />\n但影完出嚟，個海面係好多紋， 一啲都唔平。<br />\n我想問我係唔係做漏咗啲野？求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪用S mode? ISO較左幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我用咗A mode<br />\n睇返張相， 當時係ISO 80, F7.1, 25s</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25s 都唔平? 你不如 po 張相上黎睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/151106_fd55705a7eda51453e3f0ab9ba25fc4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F151106_fd55705a7eda51453e3f0ab9ba25fc4c.jpg&h=1ff25b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見笑了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得依張 ok 喇喎<br />\n佢果日係大浪都無計, 除非落 ND 再曝長d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關事<br />\n係你個海距部機太遠,長曝分別唔大<br />\n即係咁，你問下國際太空站D人，個海平唔平？<br />\n你下次響海灘近D影一張試下<br />\n個人建議可以去下三家村個海灘仔，浪越大越好，有幾舊近海既石岩set高部機避開海水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來呢個都係一個因素，學到野！"},{"pid":"1a3eed6a9daf3f2eaca6352880e018309bacbfa4","tid":23724,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91aL04q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91aL04q.jpg&h=9ea01221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時日出，我好似曝左約1分鐘<br />\n<br />\n在viewfinder睇係咁的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U22PS74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU22PS74.jpg&h=086bf124&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n👍🏻"},{"pid":"3bcaa8c9e4f136a6c248ddc998bb19d3b73ba811","tid":23724,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"ND 10000"},{"pid":"5cc4864f88469ead9894a41201148ffe0f49bc5b","tid":23724,"uid":28737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/224504_eda9292d2feed6656d6e94aef06a3a91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F224504_eda9292d2feed6656d6e94aef06a3a91.jpg&h=834c7b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影到積雪咁又點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f50759d372dc2ab45a539708cb274d1233cf697","tid":23724,"uid":49858,"like":0,"dislik